menu "Project HomeKit esp32 example"

    config SYSTEMSTATE_LED_GPIO
        int "system state led GPIO number"
        range 0 34
        default 2
        help
            GPIO number (IOxx) to system state led.
            Some GPIOs are used for other purposes (flash connections, etc.) and cannot be used to system state led.
            GPIOs 35-39 are input-only so cannot be used as outputs.

endmenu